    "We wander along its well-kept paths, pausing to admire the delicate petals arrayed in a kaleidoscope of color, each bush an individual masterpiece, the result of careful tending and nurturing. The murmuring of fellow visitors serenades us as they, too, meander through the paths, cameras in hand, capturing snapshots of nature's unassuming beauty." /
